      "content": "but \"resistance\" sounds so exhausting. it feels like i'm just being told to suffer more for no reason. if it's all so inevitable, why is it better to endure the pain of watching everything fail than to just... not be a part of it anymore? it seems more logical to just step away before it all gets even worse.",
